    "This implies a challenge in the generalization capability of existing multilingual LLMs to low-resource languages.",
    "This is further evidenced by (Cahyawijaya et al., 2023b), which extends the exploration to 12 lowresource and extremely low-resource languages, where both existing zero-shot prompting LLMs and fine-tuned pre-trained LMs struggle to outperform classical machine learning baselines, which is indicative of LLMs' limited ability to generalize to extremely low-resource languages that are 2024) for lower-resource languages.",
